                            <comment id="15270808" author="risdenk" created="Wed, 4 May 2016 15:17:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This cleans up a few other items related to Metrics as well.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;getValue returns Number instead of double&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Removes serializable.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Removes unnecessary boxing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Tests pass locally for me for solr.client.solrj.io.*&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
